  "id": "RAW_24ccb0ba",
  "title": "Claude 能直接操控你的电脑微信了，这才是真正的上位小龙虾。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647680984&idx=1&sn=ecbe236bf31aa18fcff2e1fcdd56f9a7",
  "date": "2026-03-25 02:09:00",
