  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨天，Claude凌晨的时候，新发了一个更新。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4907235621521336\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1078\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"284\" data-imgfileid=\"500197297\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8fa569bd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVUlv1SP1jGwDswtxtpddmpiccLaHgiaSRbiaxxUSibqPu0G0XaY2kSn2bOicX3vCmH5iaKwPx3qNWGzRTfPjjkzOcttUHMEzpBeQo30%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以让Claude，通过Computer use，纯视觉的方案，来对你的电脑进行操控。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个意义极度重大，不亚于当时豆包手机出来的时候，对一众没有开放自己权限的三方APP的冲击。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">最简单同时也是最牛逼的用法，就是，你可以用Claude，来直接操控你的电脑微信了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">比如，我一句话，就可以把我桌面上的文件，再随便配上一句话，发给我的微信联系人。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2394366197183098\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"497\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"497\" data-height=\"616\" data-backw=\"497\" data-backh=\"616\" data-imgfileid=\"500197331\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b2076c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqXpPRL6HJ9WsakBFAicOdy0BBfdBLEODejujGlPDtqn6n6PK6mG22JBAX58g5icZFJB4zr4kURXS1aaknLD5b4wRFvRWv6HyISqM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整个过程，Claude真的非常有条理地挨个发消息。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22734375\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 131px;\" data-width=\"2648\" data-height=\"639\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/2jjfQoZLoqXGUsricgvtAc0iaBk0Vuz3z1qpE8HBkvEqwS9kALFicibA9veRZ9TdTy9x2XFfUqpHY1Kpias6SB6N3odSOK52z3Hh12ahcqffdmlk/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"2648\" data-cropy1=\"36.650519031141876\" data-cropy2=\"636.8027681660901\" data-imgfileid=\"500197332\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0ab71379&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2jjfQoZLoqWibp9XziaNiaRLRvZF3HxCIMOicbeEibsPkmqSJbh0BG2TP2ywBH3WDDXCCw2TfytbiaAx5ia2ibdJJrXGz3RZ0QM9icM0MUK3NFtwGVOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Claude摇身一变，成为了真正的小龙虾。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实很多人不知道，小龙虾刚出来时候的名字，其实不叫OpenClaw，叫Clawdbot。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它的吉祥物和图标大家都知道了，是个龙虾，所以大家才叫它小龙虾。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4617314930991217\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"797\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197298\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ef2d83f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUzibJSkicHzSfuWEkYTakmYoYuN6eZbfdeXFJG3n7rVXJXTDvJiaasPrTs7D0Irib1ibyWkbRNJRoHUbtSE4plbb2vQlKSXVTMa5I8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">但鲜少有人知道，当今最牛逼的、属于夯上天、但是被名字耽误了的最牛逼的Agent产品，也就是Claude Code，他的吉祥物，其实是8-bit像素风格的小螃蟹，而名字就叫，Clawd。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.190556492411467\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"593\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197299\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=da7c9bab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqWwAPfEjBicj31lml5fKomDHdFXONfSZtwjGDovw1vVBa3pgqiclTdvnVnf0PwPHBfDUDFBibzRcPN01o1L8gYVEs8R7w9xv7WE00%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">所以之前小龙虾把自己叫做Clawdbot，还说自己是Agent的时候，给Anthropic气的直接给皮特发律师函，说你个狗东西必须给我改名字。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">peter也知道自己理亏，蹭的确实有点狠了，于是自己只能改成了moltbot，然后又改成了OpenClaw，大概就是这个路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">所以你就能看到，为啥</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Anthropic屌都不屌OpenClaw，最近每个月的更新几乎都刀刀砍在OpenClaw的命脉上，就是这个原因。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Claude，才是当今最屌的那个Agent，没有之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而最近的这两个更新，一个是电脑的视觉能力Computer Use，一个是真正的远程操控Dispatch。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这两个的王炸组合，又把Claude的Agent体验和能力，又带上了一个新的台阶。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里我先做个简单的科普。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是过去，不管是Claude Code、Codex、OpenClaw等等，几乎都是纯粹的直接代码驱动，跳过了前端界面，直接去操作底层的东西。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个方式的好处是精准、快速、可靠，坏处是，它只能操作那些开放了接口的东西。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以你要是只算命令行加浏览器的话，电脑上大概80%的事情其实AI已经能帮你搞定了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但那剩下的20%呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就比如你的微信、你的剪映、你电脑上那些五花八门的本地软件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些东西不在浏览器里，也没有接口，也没有CLI版，AI根本没有办法操控。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，你很少看到，玩小龙虾的人，能用小龙虾操控一些电脑的三方软件，更多的都是PPT、Excel、Word、发个文件啥的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">而Computer Use，就是来补上这最后一块拼图的，它让Claude，能看见你的屏幕了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但这里有一个非常关键的点，我必须说清楚，Computer Use不是来替代命令行和API的，它们其实是完全互补的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像人，可以凭借自己的肢体也就是眼睛+手去完成一些事情，但是在很多时候，你还是需要借助比如锤子、电钻啥的这样的省力的工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Computer Use就是人的眼睛+手，CLI的那套，就是纯粹的工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这块手机比较好感知点，我之前写miclaw的时候说过，miclaw走的是Tool Use路线，也就是API，把系统应用封装成工具让Agent调用，所以快、成功率高，但是其他APP如果不给API或者MCP的话，就没办法操作了。</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而之前的豆包手机很牛逼，在很多时候，走的是纯视觉Agent方案，读屏识别，学人模拟点击，兼容性和通用性很高，能越过高墙，缺点是慢一点步骤长一点。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这两条路线未来必然殊途同归。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再加上上周更新的Dispatch，Claude，终于变得完整了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Dispatch这个东西，就是一个更方便的远程控制，不像之前的/remote-control命令，只能在特定的终端里面不能断，现在，只要你的电脑没关，你就可以跟小龙虾一样，直接通过手机来在电脑上启动任意任务，之前只能启动Cowork，但是后面立马就把Claude Code给支持了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8571428571428571\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"595\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197300\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e63dbfd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUsckAfzMf4bHM95B5ED1h8O1iciaDVsMTkYc1lp4yS1FKmd2hwOZvvibYmyR9OWWsfxPXnpD4FQsITGmf6zDicxeNACqs29rjn8H0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这两玩意一组合，真的就起飞了，能把小龙虾摁在地上打。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">用起来也非常简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第一步，先把电脑上的Claude应用更新到最新版本。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6935185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1222\" data-height=\"847\" data-imgfileid=\"500197301\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bdcd4fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUibV4uIpdSH46yerICHibb8KoIVuFtBwfjHSaSm538NsEOYGEl1FhUcoFTYjlhldJgkuygnQcicmpzqGoqvC0iaDANd2j6YF7lOHI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点左下角头像进入到设置页面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在Desktop app下面的General里，你会看到一个Computer Use的开关。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6601851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1258\" data-height=\"830\" data-imgfileid=\"500197302\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2c396bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLo